item.title: WEEK 1 REFLECTION
item.description: At the beginning The first week in Cyber Sec Studio let me know a new world of network which is sophisticated, sapiential, dangerous and full of unknows. Under the help with friendly mates in the studio, this would be a great chance to dive deeper in the internet, and to learn and see how cyber things work. Because cyber-attacks always happen all around the world, so that cyber security become more and more important.
